data.description: Over 4000 sqft of absolutely gorgeous living space, situated in the tree-lined streets of Catawba Hill. Close to all including the wonderful Sandhill Plaza, which boasts a movie theater, restaurants, and some of your favorite retail stores. This house has all the ingredients for beautiful living: 5 bedrooms, 3 baths, 2 car garage, a large backyard with a covered double patio, and a play area for the children; on the second floor a huge media room, huge owner's suite with massive and separate his and her walk-in closets as well as a huge laundry room with lots of cabinet space. The front entry showcases a beautiful long foyer which leads directly to the straight-scissor staircase; and exposes beautiful archways on the right and throughout the main floor. All of this and more! Welcome Home to 34 Corinth CT.   The seller is offering 3000.00 toward closing costs!
